# Day4ai Cross-Functional AI Agent Infrastructure

Build a self-hosted AI agent team on the existing Hostinger VPS using **n8n** as the orchestration backbone, powered by **Gemini** and **Claude** APIs. Three C-suite agents — Chief of Staff, Chief Automation Officer, and Chief Strategy Officer — will operate as always-on business partners for Day4ai's portfolio of ventures (FairScreen, OpenClaw/ClawDeploy, D&D Sim4Fun, and future projects).

---

