1. **Infrastructure first**: Docker Compose stack on VPS (n8n + PostgreSQL + Qdrant)
2. **Agent prompts**: Write and polish system prompts for all 3 agents
3. **Chat interface**: Build the webhook-based chat workflow in n8n
4. **Daily briefing**: Build the CoS scheduled briefing workflow
5. **Strategy session**: Build the CSO deep-dive workflow
